&nbsp;  
<P class=MsoNormal style="BACKGROUND: #fbfcfd; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">中投二号</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">国新控股</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">22</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">日挂牌</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">已现身五矿系整合</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">利好：央企重组概念</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">影响系数：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">★★★★</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> <BR></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">媒体今日报道称，接近国务院国资委的权威人士透露，有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">中投二号</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">之称的中国国新控股有限责任公司</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">(</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">下称：国新控股</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">)</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">定于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">22</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">日挂牌。值得注意的是，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">中投二号</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">国新控股公司与五矿股份已</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">牵手</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”——</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">国新控股的身影已赫然出现在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">五矿系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">整合的股东名单之中。上述接近国资委人士表示：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">国新控股的职能很宽泛，只要是国资委的事它都可以参与。入股五矿重组，其主要目的是协助中国五矿股权多元化，并推动五矿整体上市。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">按这一思路推断，国新控股很有可能成为具有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">类</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">PE”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">性质的股权持有者，帮助央企整体上市和退出，可能是国新控股成立后的主要职能之一。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><BR></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">中央农村工作会议今日开幕</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">现代农业或成重要内容</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">利好：农业股、水利股</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">影响系数：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">★★★★★</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> <BR></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">从农业部获悉，继中央经济工作会议后，中央农村工作会议于今日拉开帷幕，会议将明确明年中央农村工作的目标和任务，并形成</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">2011</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">年中央</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">一号文件</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">的主要内容。近期召开的中央经济工作会议，已将</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">推进现代农业、确保农产品有效供给</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">列为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">2011</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">年的六大任务之一，并将该项任务排在第二的重要位置。多个机构和专家预测，曾在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">2010</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">一号文件</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">中重点着墨的水利和种业，有望继续成为明年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">一号文件</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">聚焦点。我国种子行业主要上市公司有登海种业、隆平高科、万向德农、丰乐种业、荃银高科、敦煌种业、禾嘉股份等</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">7</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana">家。水利设备行业主要有大禹节水、粤
